{
  "stem": "24615.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One time, the-- the Judenrat, you know, they took us to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the-- on the ice-- you know, it was like the Canadian-- between Detroit and Windsor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It really froze.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to make holes in the ice, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had an ax.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had a saw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, we had to saw the-- the ice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was two Germans for a while, watching us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one German-- he was a-- a real Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to call him the [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Brazilop ?] Commandant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "See, what they used to take away-- they took away from the Jewish people the cows, the goats, the sheep, everything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everything, they took away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he-- he took care on it, you know, this commandant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He used to kill a Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he used to come into the ghetto, and he said he just killed a dog, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So-- and he was there while we were working on the ice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he-- and he took us all, and we had to lift up a tank-- a Russian tank, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He examined it-- you know, the machines, or the motors, and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were-- we were afraid, you know, he might shoot us, so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But he didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The bullets, you know, were like gold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, and the gun was right [INAUDIBLE], you are a tall guy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And after, the Ukrainian killed him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And when they killed him, he-- he-- the Gestapo came right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And before he died, he said, a Jewish person didn't kill him, because they would kill all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They killed him because he took the cattle from them, he took the horses, he took everything from them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But anyway, so then we didn't have nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
